# arvo

Numeric primitives for hilavitkutin and consumers. L0 of the arvo
stack. Const-generic fixed-point (`UFixed`, `IFixed`), float wrappers
(`FastFloat`, `StrictFloat`), strategy markers (`Hot`/`Warm`/`Cold`/
`Precise`), composable traits, the opaque-bit storage primitive
`Bits<const N: u8, S>` (with the bit-size aliases `Bit`/`Nibble`/
`Byte`/`Word`/`DWord`/`QWord` and the `Bitfield` packed-layout
primitive), the `IBits` / `FBits` / `Width` ConstParamTy meta-
newtypes, and the `Uint*` / `Int*` numeric alias surface. Wider
contracts (`HasBitWidth`, `BitAccess`, `BitSequence`, `BitLogic`)
live in arvo-bits L1. `#![no_std]`, no alloc.
